T02TD2925E:325a-1: a'arya badzra bi d'a ra na n'a ma dh'a ra n'i s'a dha nam sa kalpam /
T02TD2925E:325a-3: 'phags pa rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa zhes bya ba'i gzungs kyi sgrub thabs cho ga zhi ba mo dang bcas pa /
T02TD2925E:325a-4: 'phags pa rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2925E:325a-5: rin chen lta bu don bdun ldan pas rang don sku gcig mi shigs rdo rjer ldan //
T02TD2925E:325a-6: gzhan don rdo rjes 'joms pas gnyis med rdo rje'i sku gnyis snang //
T02TD2925E:325a-7: thams cad rnam pa kun mchog ldan zhing mi phyed mi shigs pa //
T02TD2925E:325a-8: gdug pa 'dul phyir rdo rje'i sku ste 'jigs byed zung la 'dud //
T02TD2925E:325a-9: bya ba'i rgyud mchog rtog pa bye brag rdo rje rigs kyi don //
T02TD2925E:325a-10: bdag gzhan don rnams rdzogs byed sangs rgyas kyis gsungs te //
T02TD2925E:325a-11: bla ma rgyal de grub brnyes byin rlabs de thob 'di yi zhal mthong ste //
T02TD2925E:325a-12: gnang ba byin dang ldan pas bdag nyid bram ze gzhon nu ste //
T02TD2925E:325a-13: rig sngags ma lus 'chad 'gyur 'di bsgoms nus thob la //
T02TD2925E:325a-14: slob ma sangs rgyas gsang bas bskul phyir 'di bshad bya //
T02TD2925E:325a-15: gang zhig 'di la dad mos nas //
T02TD2925E:325a-16: bsgrubs nas yon tan rdo rje 'byung //
T02TD2925E:325a-17: 'di yi dgongs pa'i bsam yas kyang //
T02TD2925E:325a-18: lhun po ri rab zom rgyud du //
T02TD2925E:325a-19: de bzhin gshegs pas 'di skad gsungs //
T02TD2925E:325a-20: sngon gyi 'phrul pa la brten nas //
T02TD2925E:325a-21: ma 'ongs man ngag rnam gnyis te //
T02TD2925E:325a-22: bdag don rdo rje'i bsnyen pa dang //
T02TD2925E:325a-23: gzhan don rdo rje'i las sbyor bcas //
T02TD2925E:325a-24: de tsam ma bshad do zhe na //
T02TD2925E:325a-25: gang dag tu ni rang nyid kyi //
T02TD2925E:325a-26: las kyi cho ga med pa las //
T02TD2925E:325a-27: de bzhin phyi yi rgyud chen las //
T02TD2925E:325a-28: gsungs pa'i cho ga 'dir bstan bya //
T02TD2925E:325a-29: de yi dus ni bzang zhing shis pa la //
T02TD2925E:325a-30: rdo rje'i gnas te bkra shis zhi gnas su //
T02TD2925E:325b-0: bar chad zhi @325b sogs kun byas rdo rje'i g-yog dam dang //
T02TD2925E:325b-1: rdo rje sgrub po shes rab la sogs lung las bsngags pa ni //
T02TD2925E:325b-2: bya ba'i dbang dang dam tshig man ngag rab shes des /
T02TD2925E:325b-3: lus dang ngag sems gtsang zhing yid dge bas //
T02TD2925E:325b-4: rdo rje sbyor ba kun dang ldan pas bsgrub //
T02TD2925E:325b-5: sa phyogs rab tu nyams dga' bar //
T02TD2925E:325b-6: sa yi tshig kun shes nas //
T02TD2925E:325b-7: ba yi rnam lnga dri bcas pas //
T02TD2925E:325b-8: mandal sngon po me tog bcas //
T02TD2925E:325b-9: der ni rten rnams ldan pa dang //
T02TD2925E:325b-10: mchod pa lnga dang mchod yon bcas //
T02TD2925E:325b-11: khrus kyi bum pa bzang po dang /
T02TD2925E:325b-12: lha yi bum pa bzang por bya //
T02TD2925E:325b-13: de yang gser sogs dag las 'byung //
T02TD2925E:325b-14: mtshan nyid ldan der chu klung chu //
T02TD2925E:325b-16: rin chen snying po me tog bcas //
T02TD2925E:325b-17: shel dang pha lam mu tig dang //
T02TD2925E:325b-18: kha rgyan mgul gsum pa yis bcang //
T02TD2925E:325b-19: d'ur ba bdun dang ku sha dang //
T02TD2925E:325b-20: rma bya'i sgro dang rdo rjer ldan //
T02TD2925E:325b-21: las kyi cho ga mthong ba yis //
T02TD2925E:325b-22: legs byas bskrad la sgrub rdzas ni //
T02TD2925E:325b-23: rin chen snod kyi steng du gnas //
T02TD2925E:325b-24: mandal steng du de gzhag la //
T02TD2925E:325b-25: ras sogs gtsang ma gon pa yis //
T02TD2925E:325b-26: phyi rol khrus kyi rdzing bu ni //
T02TD2925E:325b-27: nyams dga' der ni nyin phyed na //
T02TD2925E:325b-28: khrus bya der yangs rab bsngags //
T02TD2925E:325b-29: stong pas dri ma rnam par sbyang //
T02TD2925E:325b-30: der song khro bos khro bo bsdu la //
T02TD2925E:325b-31: se gol sngags kyis bgegs bskrad la //
T02TD2925E:325b-32: chu de lag g-yon gsum du gtor //
T02TD2925E:325b-33: spyi bor gcig gzhag kha bshal te //
T02TD2925E:325b-35: de bzhin bum pas snga bar bya //
T02TD2925E:325b-36: bud med sha chang la sogs ni //
T02TD2925E:325b-37: ku ba'i bras ni rnam lnga spang //
T02TD2925E:325b-38: bshang sogs mi gtsang sbyor ba la //
T02TD2925E:325b-39: mnol ba med par sprul nas ni //
T02TD2925E:325b-40: de yi sngags dang phyag rgyas gdab //
T02TD2925E:325b-41: thams cad nyes par mi 'gyur ro //
T02TD2925E:325b-42: gtsang khang nyams dgar log nas ni //
T02TD2925E:325b-43: se gol 'chi med khro bos bskrad //
T02TD2925E:325b-44: rdo rjes sgo gcod stan yang ni //
T02TD2925E:325b-45: 'jam pa der ku shar ldan pa la //
T02TD2925E:325b-46: nub tu kha bltas brtan par gnas //
T02TD2925E:325b-47: skad cig mi phyed phyag rdor gyis //
T02TD2925E:325b-48: rnam 'joms dpag med rab bstan nas //
T02TD2925E:325b-49: skrod pa'i phyag rgyas sngags rdo rje //
T02TD2925E:325b-50: phyag 'tshal nas ni gtor byed par //
T02TD2925E:325b-51: rnam snang khro bo gnyis ldan pas //
T02TD2925E:325b-52: tshangs la sogs pa'i gdon sogs bskrad //
T02TD2925E:326a-2: bar chad bgegs kyis mi tshugs so //
T02TD2925E:326a-3: rnam 'joms yang snying dri chab kyis //
T02TD2925E:326a-4: 'byor pa bsangs te skad cig gis //
T02TD2925E:326a-5: mchod pa dag par bya phyir brlab //
T02TD2925E:326a-6: de nas mdun gyi nam mkha' la //
T02TD2925E:326a-7: sangs rgyas gnyis dang 'jigs byed drug / de la yid kyi las kun bya //
T02TD2925E:326a-8: rang bzhin rnam dag sngags kyis ni //
T02TD2925E:326a-9: nyams dang stong pa'i ye shes bya //
T02TD2925E:326a-10: rin chen khang pa yid 'ong ste //
T02TD2925E:326a-11: rdo rje'i brag tu rnam par bsam //
T02TD2925E:326a-12: der ni lha chen drag por bya //
T02TD2925E:326a-13: bdag nyid 'jigs pa'i nga rgyal gyis //
T02TD2925E:326a-15: gsol gdab rdo rje'i bsam gtan gnyis //
T02TD2925E:326a-17: rdo rje'i rnam par bsam sngags brjod //
T02TD2925E:326a-18: bdag don rdo rje stong pa'i lha //
T02TD2925E:326a-19: de nas gzhan don yi ge ste //
T02TD2925E:326a-20: thog med las ni gsal ba ste //
T02TD2925E:326a-21: de la yig gnyis sngo spras pa //
T02TD2925E:326a-22: nus ldan yi ge'i lha yin no //
T02TD2925E:326a-23: de la rdo rje sngags kyi sgra //
T02TD2925E:326a-24: stong pa mtshon byed khams rnams su //
T02TD2925E:326a-25: dam pa gnyis byas de la bstim //
T02TD2925E:326a-26: de ni sgra'i lha zhes bya ste //
T02TD2925E:326a-27: de gyur dam pa kun thim pas //
T02TD2925E:326a-28: rdo rje nyi ma la gnas pa'i //
T02TD2925E:326a-29: phyag na rdo rje gsang ba'i bdag / stobs chen khro bo 'jigs cha byad //
T02TD2925E:326a-30: sngo nag rdo rje sdigs mdzub can //
T02TD2925E:326a-31: ral pa la sogs kun ldan pas //
T02TD2925E:326a-32: 'byung po bsdigs pa gzugs brnyan tshul //
T02TD2925E:326a-33: 'di ni gzugs kyi lha zhes grags //
T02TD2925E:326a-34: de nas de ni gsal brtan phyir //
T02TD2925E:326a-35: ri bo 'bigs pa'i phyag rgya dang //
T02TD2925E:326a-36: rdo rje yan lag 'bar ba yi //
T02TD2925E:326a-37: sngags kyis spyi bo sogs bzhag pas //
T02TD2925E:326a-38: gtsug tor la sogs grub cing bsrung //
T02TD2925E:326a-39: de yang phyag rgya'i lha ru bstan //
T02TD2925E:326a-40: de nas dus ni thams cad du //
T02TD2925E:326a-41: de dang mi 'bral kun byed pa //
T02TD2925E:326a-42: mtshan ma'am rnam rtog lha zhes gsungs //
T02TD2925E:326a-43: ye shes lnga dang sku gsum dang //
T02TD2925E:326a-44: don gnyis grub cing 'od dang ni //
T02TD2925E:326a-45: rdzu 'phrul nus pa ston byed pas //
T02TD2925E:326a-46: lha zhes sh'akya mchog gis gsungs //
T02TD2925E:326a-47: de nas bum pa mi dmigs las //
T02TD2925E:326a-48: rin chen khang par 'dam skye sa bzhi //
T02TD2925E:326a-49: ge sar sogs la bsil rdo rje //
T02TD2925E:326a-50: rdo rje man ngag ldan par bsam //
T02TD2925E:326a-51: dbus su sprin sgra gyur pa las //
T02TD2925E:326b-0: phyag na rdo rje thugs kyi mchog / rdo rje rnam @326b 'joms khro bo ni //
T02TD2925E:326b-1: bdag mtshungs las kyi rdo rje la //
T02TD2925E:326b-2: zla ba med pa bsnams pa'o //
T02TD2925E:326b-3: de yi mdun du m'a ma k'i //
T02TD2925E:326b-4: sngo zhing dga' ldan autpal sngo //
T02TD2925E:326b-6: dran pa bzhi las byung ba ni //
T02TD2925E:326b-7: kun kyang rim min cig car ro //
T02TD2925E:326b-8: shar lho rdo rje k'i la ni //
T02TD2925E:326b-9: sngo dmar 'jigs pa kun ldan la //
T02TD2925E:326b-10: rdo rje phur bu g-yas na ste //
T02TD2925E:326b-11: g-yon pa kun ni bsdigs par mdzad //
T02TD2925E:326b-12: lho nub rdo rje be con te //
T02TD2925E:326b-13: sdo nag rdo rje be con no //
T02TD2925E:326b-14: nub byang rdo rje tho ba ste //
T02TD2925E:326b-15: sdo skye de bzhin 'jigs pa la //
T02TD2925E:326b-16: rdo rjes mtshan pa'i tho ba ste //
T02TD2925E:326b-17: byang shar rdo rje gtum po ni //
T02TD2925E:326b-18: mig sman mdog 'dra rdo rje ni //
T02TD2925E:326b-19: rtse gcig bsnams par rab tu bsgom //
T02TD2925E:326b-20: kun kyang tsham ngam bdud bzhi 'joms //
T02TD2925E:326b-21: de rnams ye shes lnga ldan rigs //
T02TD2925E:326b-22: dbu la mi bskyod mgon po ni //
T02TD2925E:326b-23: ral pa'i thor tshugs bzhad khro ba //
T02TD2925E:326b-24: dpa' bo dag la rnam par gsungs //
T02TD2925E:326b-27: rig pa rig ma dam tshig can //
T02TD2925E:326b-28: dpag med byon gyur mi 'chi ba //
T02TD2925E:326b-29: thugs ka nas bton des bskrad bcad //
T02TD2925E:326b-30: de la rang sngags bskul bcas kyis //
T02TD2925E:326b-31: mchod yon bzang po nyer bstan pa //
T02TD2925E:326b-32: mi shigs phyag rgya rang sngags lngas //
T02TD2925E:326b-33: so so la ni gnyis med zhugs //
T02TD2925E:326b-34: phyogs skyong 'khor gyi phyi rim du'o //
T02TD2925E:326b-35: de nas dam tshig bstan bya'i phyir //
T02TD2925E:326b-36: de bzhin mi phyed khros pa yis //
T02TD2925E:326b-37: rigs kyi yum gyis rgyas btab pas //
T02TD2925E:326b-38: de yang rig pa rnam pa gnyis //
T02TD2925E:326b-39: mtha' med par du zhugs phyir ro //
T02TD2925E:326b-40: bdag ni dam tshig ldan pa las //
T02TD2925E:326b-41: ye shes mi 'jug mtho dman tshul //
T02TD2925E:326b-42: de yang bya ba kun nas gsungs //
T02TD2925E:326b-43: de nas mchod pa rnam pa lnga //
T02TD2925E:326b-44: kun gyi rigs la de rigs dbul //
T02TD2925E:326b-45: sgra dang bzang po de bzhin no //
T02TD2925E:326b-46: thal mo sbyar nas gus pa yis //
T02TD2925E:326b-47: rdo rje bsnams la bstod pa yin //
T02TD2925E:326b-48: gang gi rang bzhin chags sdang rnam bral yang//
T02TD2925E:326b-49: gdul bya gdul phyir khro la khro ba dang //
T02TD2925E:326b-50: 'dod chags can la chags can ltar ston pa //
T02TD2925E:326b-51: byang chub mchog gnas de la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD2925E:326b-52: gang zhig las dang rnam smin mkhyen pa yis //
T02TD2925E:326b-53: 'gro ba kun dang ji ltar mthun pa yi //
T02TD2925E:327a-0: gsang sngags gzugs kyis rjes su 'jug @327a * //
T02TD2925E:327a-2: sngags kyi rnam 'dren de la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD2925E:327a-3: nad gcod bdud 'joms mi rtog bzhi las byung //
T02TD2925E:327a-4: las rnams 'joms mdzad khro bo 'bar bar snang //
T02TD2925E:327a-5: nor bu rin chen lta bur gdul bya gdul //
T02TD2925E:327a-6: khro bo khyed rnams la ni bstod phyag 'tshal //
T02TD2925E:327a-7: rig pa skyong ba'i lha rnams la //
T02TD2925E:327a-8: tshigs bcad bcu yis bstod pa yin //
T02TD2925E:327a-9: de nas 'dod pa'i don gsol gdab //
T02TD2925E:327a-10: de ltar bya ba rab rdzogs pas //
T02TD2925E:327a-11: don dang tshig gi lhar gnas shing //
T02TD2925E:327a-12: bya ba rigs dang gdul bya'i phyir //
T02TD2925E:327a-13: bya rgyud rig pa 'dzin sde ste //
T02TD2925E:327a-14: der gnas sngags kyi bzlas bya ba //
T02TD2925E:327a-15: nor bu'i phreng ba'i bskul sngags kyis //
T02TD2925E:327a-16: byin rlabs lag pas legs gzungs te //
T02TD2925E:327a-17: mig gi lha thugs zla ba la //
T02TD2925E:327a-18: rdo rje gyes pa h'um gnas bsam //
T02TD2925E:327a-19: lce rtse mi g-yo gzhan mi thos //
T02TD2925E:327a-20: yid kyis sngags kyi sgrar gnas pa //
T02TD2925E:327a-21: rdo rje'i sngags ni rgyas bsdus gsum //
T02TD2925E:327a-22: mos pa gcig ni bzlas par bya //
T02TD2925E:327a-23: thugs bskul bdag gzhan don rdzogs nas //
T02TD2925E:327a-24: sems can khams sbyangs sems can che //
T02TD2925E:327a-25: byin rlabs rnam gnyis de gnas bsdu //
T02TD2925E:327a-26: don rnams rab tu rdzogs byed pas //
T02TD2925E:327a-27: zab mo bdag gi spyod yul te //
T02TD2925E:327a-28: sgra la gnas pa'i bzlas pa de //
T02TD2925E:327a-29: mi tshig g-yal dang dri ngan sogs //
T02TD2925E:327a-30: bar chad ngan pa spangs la bsgrub //
T02TD2925E:327a-31: de yang dam bcas bar du'o //
T02TD2925E:327a-33: khrus byas kha bshal phyag rdor gyi //
T02TD2925E:327a-34: yi ge brgya pas gsol gdab 'jug / thun drug sbyor ba de ltar bya //
T02TD2925E:327a-35: khrus gsum bya dang gos brje sogs //
T02TD2925E:327a-36: bya ba las gsungs rgyas par bya//
T02TD2925E:327a-37: tha mar nor bu bum pa dbul //
T02TD2925E:327a-38: bsrung la ngo mtshar tshul du gang //
T02TD2925E:327a-39: bshang sogs spyod lam de bzhin bya //
T02TD2925E:327a-40: zas la bdud rtsir byin brlabs te //
T02TD2925E:327a-41: dbul dang bza' bas tshim pa'o //
T02TD2925E:327a-42: 'khor lo gtor ma gtang ba yang //
T02TD2925E:327a-43: bdag byas cho ga bzhin du'o //
T02TD2925E:327a-44: de ltar yon tan tshang ba yis //
T02TD2925E:327a-45: mthong dang rig pa'i mtshan ma 'byung //
T02TD2925E:327a-46: lha yi rten bzhad mthong sogs dang //
T02TD2925E:327a-47: lus bde mngon sum la sogs so //
T02TD2925E:327a-48: de ltar grub pas gang byas kyang //
T02TD2925E:327a-49: grub ste gzhan du nyams par 'gyur //
T02TD2925E:327a-50: rtag tu de byed rnal 'byor pa //
T02TD2925E:327a-51: rdo rje'i sku ni nges par 'grub //
T02TD2925E:327b-0: rdo rje'i las kun smos @327b ci dgos //
T02TD2925E:327b-1: de nas dkyil 'khor gshegs mchod dang //
T02TD2925E:327b-2: bzod gsol dam tshig bsdu byas la //
T02TD2925E:327b-3: mandal legs par byi dor bya //
T02TD2925E:327b-4: lhag gnyis dpa' bo gcig pa ni //
T02TD2925E:327b-5: 'byor pa chung bar shes par bya //
T02TD2925E:327b-6: de nas sgrub pa'i las sbyar te //
T02TD2925E:327b-7: nad la sogs pa zhi bya dang //
T02TD2925E:327b-8: las kyi tshogs rnams sgrub pa'o //
T02TD2925E:327b-9: rdo rje khrus kyis dag bya ba //
T02TD2925E:327b-10: rgyas par dag byas khrus las shes //
T02TD2925E:327b-11: bdag gam gzhan dag sdug bsngal sogs //
T02TD2925E:327b-12: ldan pa bsal phyir 'di dag brtsam //
T02TD2925E:327b-13: rdo rje slob dpon slob ma ni //
T02TD2925E:327b-14: gos gtsang khrus bya dkar gsum bza' //
T02TD2925E:327b-15: shin tu spyod lam gtsang ba yis //
T02TD2925E:327b-16: nang gi sdom pa bsnyen gnas sogs //
T02TD2925E:327b-17: rten gyis blangs te bdag gzhi can //
T02TD2925E:327b-18: de dag sta gon gnas pa ste //
T02TD2925E:327b-19: zhag gcig nyi ma la sogs bya //
T02TD2925E:327b-20: de nas sa yi las byas te //
T02TD2925E:327b-21: gtor ma rgyas pa gsungs pa bzhin //
T02TD2925E:327b-22: bslang la sogs ni sngags dag dang //
T02TD2925E:327b-23: bsam gtan dag gis cung zad yin//
T02TD2925E:327b-25: rten gyi dkyil 'khor tshul du bya //
T02TD2925E:327b-27: byug pas legs byugs khru bzhi pa //
T02TD2925E:327b-28: dge ba'i ras kyis thig btab nas //
T02TD2925E:327b-29: bkra shis tshon gyi 'khor lo ni //
T02TD2925E:327b-30: lte ba rtsibs bzhi la sogs bri //
T02TD2925E:327b-31: mtshan ma kun ni nges par dgod//
T02TD2925E:327b-32: sgo la phyag rgya bzhi yang ngo //
T02TD2925E:327b-33: las kyi cho ga shes par bya //
T02TD2925E:327b-34: legs par nub tu sgo dbye'o //
T02TD2925E:327b-35: lhag chad gso zhing de rgyan du //
T02TD2925E:327b-36: mda' sogs 'phen dang rgyal mtshan gdugs //
T02TD2925E:327b-37: lnga ldi phreng bas nyams dgar mdzes //
T02TD2925E:327b-38: gong du gsungs pa'i bum pa gcig / khri la dbus su gnas par bya //
T02TD2925E:327b-39: mtshams bzhi de bzhin bum pa bzhi //
T02TD2925E:327b-40: bdag khrus bum pa nub tu'o //
T02TD2925E:327b-41: de nas rgyas par sngon bzhin du //
T02TD2925E:327b-42: khrus byas gsol gdab par bya'o //
T02TD2925E:327b-43: bum pa'i rdo rje thag bzung nas //
T02TD2925E:327b-44: bsam gtan sngon bzhin ldan pa yis //
T02TD2925E:327b-45: khro bo'i ngag tu ring thung gnyis //
T02TD2925E:327b-46: brgya rtsa brgyad dam rtsa gcig bzlas //
T02TD2925E:327b-47: las la de las mang mi dgos //
T02TD2925E:327b-48: bdag dang lha sogs 'od zer gyis //
T02TD2925E:327b-49: bsgrub bya'i 'dod sgrub byas par bsam //
T02TD2925E:327b-50: de yang lha ni rdo rje chu //
T02TD2925E:327b-51: de nas las kyi cho ga ni //
T02TD2925E:327b-52: lha yi mtshan ma dug 'joms kyis //
T02TD2925E:327b-53: phyi ste nub kyi sgo nas ni //
T02TD2925E:328a-0: shar sgor ston pa thar par @328a * //
T02TD2925E:328a-2: dbus su khri steng de nas ni //
T02TD2925E:328a-3: rnam par 'joms pas nga rgyal bya //
T02TD2925E:328a-4: dri ma dag dang ldan bsams te //
T02TD2925E:328a-5: bden pa bdar zhing bka' bsgo nas //
T02TD2925E:328a-6: sngags rnams kun du dril ba yis //
T02TD2925E:328a-7: dang por de la yungs kar gyis //
T02TD2925E:328a-8: bskrad de de nas rma bya dang //
T02TD2925E:328a-9: d'ur ba ku shas byabs pa la //
T02TD2925E:328a-10: nad sogs ma lus gdon par bya //
T02TD2925E:328a-11: de nas sngags bzlas grogs kyis ni //
T02TD2925E:328a-12: bkra shis bsgrags la chu dbang bskur //
T02TD2925E:328a-13: thams cad dag par bsam par bya //
T02TD2925E:328a-14: dung la sogs pa bkra shis sbyin //
T02TD2925E:328a-15: de nas de la lha bkod de //
T02TD2925E:328a-16: sngags kyi gnas su bsrung bar bya //
T02TD2925E:328a-17: dge ba'i las la srung 'khor ni //
T02TD2925E:328a-18: rtsibs bzhi rgyan sngags spras pa yang //
T02TD2925E:328a-19: rin po ches bris rab gnas la //
T02TD2925E:328a-20: byin rlabs bzlas te gdags par bya //
T02TD2925E:328a-21: de nas de la shel sgo nas //
T02TD2925E:328a-22: nub nas bton la rdo rje sbyin //
T02TD2925E:328a-23: rnam 'joms las kyang brlab par bya //
T02TD2925E:328a-24: de nas dbang bskur thob pa ste //
T02TD2925E:328a-25: nad la sogs pa las thar pa //
T02TD2925E:328a-26: zla ba sgra gcan las thar bzhin //
T02TD2925E:328a-27: phun sum tshogs pa'i rgyud kun ldan //
T02TD2925E:328a-28: yon tan ma lus rtsa bar 'gyur //
T02TD2925E:328a-29: bde ba kun dang ldan pa dang //
T02TD2925E:328a-30: sdug bsngal thams cad sel mdo bzhin //
T02TD2925E:328a-31: sdig las grol te byang chub mchog /
T02TD2925E:328a-32: thun mong las ni nges par 'grub //
T02TD2925E:328a-33: lan cig brtsams pas de sgrub na //
T02TD2925E:328a-34: rtag tu khrus byas smos ci dgos //
T02TD2925E:328a-35: de nas dkyil 'khor gshegs mchod la //
T02TD2925E:328a-36: bzod gsol dam tshig bsdu byas la //
T02TD2925E:328a-37: mandal legs par byi dor bya //
T02TD2925E:328a-38: lha gcig bum pa gcig pa ni //
T02TD2925E:328a-39: 'byor pa chung bas shes par bya //
T02TD2925E:328a-40: de ltar shes pa'i sgrub pa pos //
T02TD2925E:328a-41: bdag gzhan 'dod pa rdzogs don du //
T02TD2925E:328a-42: rdo rje las sngags ting 'dzin gyis //
T02TD2925E:328a-43: las rnams bsgrub par bya ba yin //
T02TD2925E:328a-44: bshad rgyud rdo rje'i zom las ni //
T02TD2925E:328a-45: rdo rje'i rtsa ba 'di ltar bkrol //
T02TD2925E:328a-46: bskrad pa la sogs bco lnga la //
T02TD2925E:328a-47: las kyi mtha' bsgyur sngags 'khor las //
T02TD2925E:328a-48: bsam gtan mkhas pas shes par bya //
T02TD2925E:328a-49: bsdu nas rnam pa bzhi ru 'gyur //
T02TD2925E:328a-50: rig sngags mnan dang rig sngags gcad //
T02TD2925E:328a-51: las gsum rmongs dang rengs pa'o //
T02TD2925E:328a-52: zhi ba la sogs las rnams ni //
T02TD2925E:328a-53: dus dang phyogs dang rdzas rnams dang //
T02TD2925E:328b-0: bsam pa @328b thabs dang lha dang sngags //
T02TD2925E:328b-2: zhi bar bya ba la sogs rnams //
T02TD2925E:328b-3: lha yi rnam pa gsum 'gyur te //
T02TD2925E:328b-4: gtso 'khor gnyis su bsdebs pa dang //
T02TD2925E:328b-5: gtso dang 'khor ni so so ste //
T02TD2925E:328b-6: kun la las kun rdzogs pa'o //
T02TD2925E:328b-7: sngags dang lha dang 'khor los shes //
T02TD2925E:328b-8: kun gyi las ni 'di ltar bya //
T02TD2925E:328b-9: zhi ba'i dus ni snga dro ste //
T02TD2925E:328b-10: shar du kha bltas dkyil 'khor la //
T02TD2925E:328b-11: brten pa'am yang na bum pa la'o //
T02TD2925E:328b-12: shin tu dge ba'i las dag las //
T02TD2925E:328b-14: rab gnas bum pa'i steng bzhag ste //
T02TD2925E:328b-15: lha rnams dkar po rnam par bsam //
T02TD2925E:328b-16: mchod pa de bzhin sngags mchog ni //
T02TD2925E:328b-17: phyag 'tshal thams cad rig pa gnas //
T02TD2925E:328b-18: zhi ba gtso ste 'khor gyi yang //
T02TD2925E:328b-19: bzhi la bod pa rab brtags te //
T02TD2925E:328b-20: kye nas blo gros bzlas pa yis //
T02TD2925E:328b-21: thams cad zhi bar bltas nas ni //
T02TD2925E:328b-22: 'khor lo lus la gdags pa yis //
T02TD2925E:328b-23: nad sogs thams cad zhi bar 'gyur //
T02TD2925E:328b-24: rgyas la ser po'i ris la ni //
T02TD2925E:328b-25: gur gum gyis ni 'khor lo bri //
T02TD2925E:328b-26: de bzhin bya ste lha rnams ser //
T02TD2925E:328b-27: sngags ni de bzhin gtso bo yi //
T02TD2925E:328b-29: de yis rgyas bsams mchod na ni //
T02TD2925E:328b-30: tshe sogs thams cad rgyas par 'gyur //
T02TD2925E:328b-31: dbang la smad 'tshong zhabs ma la//
T02TD2925E:328b-32: rgya skyegs khu bas 'khor lo bri //
T02TD2925E:328b-33: de bzhin bsam gtan dmar po la //
T02TD2925E:328b-34: sngags ni de mtshungs phur bu nas //
T02TD2925E:328b-35: phyag 'tshal bzlas pas dbang byas bsam //
T02TD2925E:328b-36: lam chen sbas na kun dbang 'gyur //
T02TD2925E:328b-37: gsad la gru gsum chos 'byung dang //
T02TD2925E:328b-38: thams cad nag byas ro ras la //
T02TD2925E:328b-39: dug la sogs pas 'khor lo bri //
T02TD2925E:328b-40: kha sbyar phye la bkug bstims nas //
T02TD2925E:328b-41: lha rnams drag pos bsad par bsam //
T02TD2925E:328b-42: sngags ni gsod pa gsad par bzlas //
T02TD2925E:328b-43: tha ma bsregs na thams cad 'chi //
T02TD2925E:328b-44: gzhan gyi rig sngags gcad pa ni //
T02TD2925E:328b-45: gi wang gis ni 'khor lo bri //
T02TD2925E:328b-46: lha kun drag por shes par bya //
T02TD2925E:328b-47: de bzhin gcad sa ming bcas dang //
T02TD2925E:328b-48: stobs chen bzlas ngag bcad par bsam //
T02TD2925E:328b-49: de nyid de yis rab gtugs na //
T02TD2925E:328b-50: des ni byad stems rig sngags kun //
T02TD2925E:328b-51: gcod byed de la the tshom med //
T02TD2925E:328b-52: rig sngags mnan la de bzhin du //
T02TD2925E:328b-53: mtshon gyi reg pas bris nas ni //
T02TD2925E:329a-2: sngags ni ming bcing bzlas bsdoms bsreg / de yi sngags rnams mnan bsams shing //
T02TD2925E:329a-3: lam chen rgya gram dag mnan na //
T02TD2925E:329a-4: nges par rig sngags kun gzhom 'gyur //
T02TD2925E:329a-5: rengs la de bzhin k'a ya stvam //
T02TD2925E:329a-6: rmongs la bi dhi mo ha'o //
T02TD2925E:329a-7: ngag rengs w'a ka stvam zhes brjod //
T02TD2925E:329a-8: skrag la bhee ra ya h'um ngo //
T02TD2925E:329a-9: 'jil ba la bha ya ka ra'o //
T02TD2925E:329a-10: 'joms la ma ta zhes pa yin //
T02TD2925E:329a-12: gdon mi za la aa mri sod //
T02TD2925E:329a-13: brlag la ta th'a ya zhes te //
T02TD2925E:329a-16: las byed karma k'a ra ya //
T02TD2925E:329a-17: ma grub grub byed karma sidhya //
T02TD2925E:329a-19: srung la raksha ku ru ste //
T02TD2925E:329a-20: gza' skar bzlog pa la sogs pa //
T02TD2925E:329a-21: man ngag ldan pa'i mkhas pas sbyar //
T02TD2925E:329a-23: bya ba bzhi ni nges shes bya //
T02TD2925E:329a-24: rdo rje lta bur thogs med pa //
T02TD2925E:329a-25: nan tan gyis ni bsgrub par bya //
T02TD2925E:329a-26: nan tan gyis ni bsgrub byas pas //
T02TD2925E:329a-27: bdag dang gzhan don nges par 'grub //
T02TD2925E:329a-28: nges par don mthong bya ba'i cho ga ni //
T02TD2925E:329a-29: brgya rtsa brgyad byas de ni 'di ches te //
T02TD2925E:329a-30: rdo rje rnam 'joms cho ga 'di sbyar bas //
T02TD2925E:329a-31: khams gsum ma lus don rnams thob par shog //
T02TD2925E:329a-32: 'phags pa rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa'i sgrub thabs cho ga zhib mo dang bcas pa /
T02TD2925E:329a-33: bram ze rig sngags 'chang ba mkhas pa chen po ku m'a ra se nas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD2925E:329a-35: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po buddha gupta dang /
T02TD2925E:329a-36: bod kyi lo ts'a ba dpa' manydzu shr'i warmas bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o /
T02TD2925E:329a-38: // / phyis pandi ta dznyon teng ha du dang /
T02TD2925E:329a-39: lo ts'a ba da 'og bsod nams mos pa shes rab kyis gsan nas zhus pa'o//
